   <body>
      <context>
         <p>Park the lift truck on a level surface, parking brake applied,
transmission in neutral.</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Raise the carriage high enough to access the drive axle hosing
level/fill plug.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Block the bottom of the carriage with a block of wood to hold
the carriage in the raised position.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Turn the ignition switch OFF. </p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_izd_ywz_5gc">
                     <image href="media/image911.png" id="image_jzd_ywz_5gc" placement="inline"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Lubricate the two fittings for the mast hinge pins, one on each
side of the mast.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
